OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly dry with some bright
OL,6,Fspells possibly developing, until a
OL,7,Fnarrow band of rain or showers moves
OL,8,Feast this afternoon. Later western
OL,9,Fareas are likely to become dry and
OL,10,Fclearer. Breezy along the coast at
OL,11,Ftimes.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClear spells for a time this
OL,14,Fevening, with temperatures quickly
OL,15,Ffalling and perhaps some patchy mist.
OL,16,FThen cloud increases with showers or
OL,17,Flonger spells of rain arriving. Also
OL,18,Fbecoming breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
