OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain,
OL,6,Fthese turning light and patchy through
OL,7,Fthe afternoon. Most places becoming
OL,8,Fdry and perhaps brighter late
OL,9,Fafternoon. Breezy inland, windy along
OL,10,Fthe coast. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBreezy
OL,13,FMonday with rain spreading east but
OL,14,Falso some drier spells. Dry Tuesday
OL,15,Fand Wednesday with light winds and
OL,16,Fbright or sunny spells. Temperatures
OL,17,Fgenerally a little above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
